#

Peanut Butter Waffles

25 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

PeanutsGlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastEasyQuick

Description

Fluffy waffles infused with creamy peanut butter, perfect for a quick breakfast or snack!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • salt: 1/4 tsp
  • milk: 1 cup
  • peanut butter: 1/3 cup
  • egg: 1
  • butter: 2 tbsp, melted
  • maple syrup: for serving
